ON MILL HILL.

296
00:24:17,150 --> 00:24:18,850
ONE YEAR.

297
00:24:18,890 --> 00:24:24,020
ONE YEAR DOWN AT WESLEYAN IS ALL
WE'VE ASKED FROM YOU, WILLIAM.

298
00:24:24,060 --> 00:24:27,790
PA! COLLEGE IS
FINE FOR ROB.

299
00:24:27,830 --> 00:24:30,860
HE'S STUDYIN'
FOR THE MINISTRY.

300
00:24:30,900 --> 00:24:33,060
I'M NO PREACHER,
AND I'M NEVER GONNA BE.

301
00:24:33,100 --> 00:24:34,870
SO WHY GO?

302
00:24:34,900 --> 00:24:39,070
