ABOUT BASEBALL ON MILL HILL.

307
00:24:54,760 --> 00:24:58,060
I HAPPEN TO KNOW THAT
BOOTLEG WHISKEY

308
00:24:58,090 --> 00:24:59,730
FLOWS LIKE WATER EVERY
SATURDAY NIGHT.

309
00:24:59,760 --> 00:25:05,130
NOW ARE YOU GOING TO DENY THAT
BASEBALL AND BOOZE GO TOGETHER?

310
00:25:05,170 --> 00:25:07,870
NO, SIR, I
CAN'T DENY THAT.

311
00:25:07,900 --> 00:25:09,000
WILLIAM, I-

312
00:25:09,040 --> 00:25:10,740
