GETTING WHAT YOU WANT.

338
00:26:41,700 --> 00:26:44,360
IT'S NOT ABOUT
BEING MISERABLE!

339
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:46,200
I GOTTA DO THIS!

340
00:26:46,230 --> 00:26:48,930
THIS IS MY
FINAL WORD.

341
00:26:53,870 --> 00:26:56,170
