373
00:30:08,400 --> 00:30:09,570
C'MON.

374
00:31:17,500 --> 00:31:20,070
WHAT DO
YA THINK?

375
00:31:20,110 --> 00:31:22,610
SURE IS A LONG
WAY DOWN.

376
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:26,080
