MIGHTY SORE LOSERS.

758
00:59:56,320 --> 00:59:57,220
JOHN DOUGLAS.

759
00:59:57,260 --> 00:59:58,620
CHICK SPANGLER.

760
00:59:58,660 --> 00:59:59,960
WILL WRIGHT.

761
00:59:59,990 --> 01:00:01,160
GLAD TO KNOW
YOU BOTH.

762
01:00:01,190 --> 01:00:03,290
BEEN TO EVERY
GAME.

763
01:00:03,330 --> 01:00:04,830
GINNIE'S HERE
IN THE TRUCK.

764
01:00:04,860 --> 01:00:06,030
OH-YOU'RE
GINNIE'S FATHER?

765
01:00:06,060 --> 01:00:08,160
THAT'S RIGHT.
I'M GINNIE'S FATHER.

766
01:00:08,200 --> 01:00:10,070
