MAKIN' BATS.

771
01:00:17,340 --> 01:00:19,210
GOOD THING
FOR US.

772
01:00:22,050 --> 01:00:23,780
GREAT GAME,
WILL!

773
01:00:24,920 --> 01:00:26,420
WHAT A HIT
THAT WAS!

774
01:00:26,450 --> 01:00:28,080
THANK YOU!

775
01:00:28,120 --> 01:00:29,950
AND YOU PITCHED
REAL WELL, CHARLES.

776
01:00:29,990 --> 01:00:31,890
THANKS.

777
01:00:31,920 --> 01:00:33,860
ALRIGHT, LET'S GET
OUTTA HERE.

778
01:00:37,460 --> 01:00:40,430
YOU BOYS RIDIN'
IN THE BACK.

779
