HAVE ONE.

782
01:01:30,000 --> 01:01:31,160
FINE.

783
01:01:31,200 --> 01:01:32,930
A WHAT?

784
01:01:32,970 --> 01:01:34,770
IT'S NOT AS BAD
AS IT SOUNDS.

785
01:01:34,800 --> 01:01:36,900
JUST COCA-COLA
WITH A SQUIRT OF LIME.

786
01:01:36,940 --> 01:01:38,110
DADDY'S FAVORITE.

787
01:01:38,140 --> 01:01:39,770
SHOELESS JOE SPECIAL!

788
01:01:39,810 --> 01:01:40,940
THAT'S RIGHT.

789
01:01:40,980 --> 01:01:44,140
NOW, THERE'S A MAN WHO COULD
TEAR THE COVER OFF A BALL.

790
01:01:44,180 --> 01:01:46,180
WAIT, YOU SAW
HIM PLAY?

791
01:01:46,220 --> 01:01:49,780
STILL SEE HIM ONCE IN A WHILE
'ROUND THE GREENVILLE AREA.

792
01:01:49,820 --> 01:01:52,290
EVEN AFTER THAT
BLACK SOX TRIAL.

793
01:01:52,320 --> 01:01:54,750
HE'LL ALWAYS BE A HERO
TO THE MILL.

794
01:01:54,790 --> 01:01:58,890
YOU KNOW THAT WHOLE SERIES
HIS BATTING AVERAGE WAS .375.

795
01:01:58,930 --> 01:02:03,030
AND HE SET A WORLD SERIES
RECORD WITH 12 HITS!

796
01:02:03,060 --> 01:02:05,300
AND THEY BANNED HIM
ALONG WITH THE TAKERS!

797
01:02:05,330 --> 01:02:08,900
ONE OF THE GREATEST PLAYERS
THAT EVER STRODE THE DIAMOND.

798
01:02:08,940 --> 01:02:10,300
HE WAS A NATURAL.

799
01:02:10,340 --> 01:02:12,240
SPEAKING OF FAMOUS
BALL PLAYERS,

800
01:02:12,270 --> 01:02:13,910
DID YOU BOYS HEAR
THAT BILLY SUNDAY'S

801
01:02:13,940 --> 01:02:16,440
