MY WHOLE LIFE!

804
01:02:19,350 --> 01:02:21,950
HE USED TO PLAY WITH
THE CHICAGO WHITE STOCKINGS.

805
01:02:21,980 --> 01:02:24,150
I'LL BE GLAD TO TAKE ANYONE
WHO CARES TO GO.

806
01:02:24,190 --> 01:02:25,150
COUNT ME IN.

807
01:02:25,190 --> 01:02:26,820
SURE.
SOUNDS INTERESTING.

808
01:02:26,860 --> 01:02:28,290
HERE WE ARE.

809
01:02:28,320 --> 01:02:29,590
THANK YOU!

810
01:02:33,460 --> 01:02:34,430
THANK YOU,
SIR.

811
01:02:34,460 --> 01:02:36,130
I HOPE YOU
ENJOY THAT.

812
01:02:41,500 --> 01:02:43,940
SAY, DO YOU THINK I COULD
COME BY THE SHOP SOMETIME

813
01:02:43,970 --> 01:02:45,370
