TURN A BAT?

814
01:02:45,410 --> 01:02:47,170
I'VE GOT ONE ON THE
LATHE RIGHT NOW.

815
01:02:47,210 --> 01:02:48,840
YOU WANNA COME
BY TONIGHT?

816
01:02:48,880 --> 01:02:50,940
SURE, OKAY!

817
01:03:06,130 --> 01:03:10,160
HE'S GOTTA GET INITIATED
JUST LIKE ANYBODY ELSE.

818
01:03:10,200 --> 01:03:13,030
WE CAN'T AFFORD
TO HURT HIM, PIKE.

819
01:03:13,070 --> 01:03:15,300
WE NEED HIM.

820
01:03:15,340 --> 01:03:18,940
HE IS BRINGING
US LUCK!

821
01:03:18,970 --> 01:03:22,380
FALLON, DIDN'T YOU GET
DRUGGED ON THE STONE STEPS

822
01:03:22,410 --> 01:03:24,910
ON YOUR BACKSIDE
YER FIRST SEASON?

823
01:03:24,950 --> 01:03:29,320
YEAH, BUT WHAT YOU
WANNA DO IS CRAZY!

824
01:03:29,350 --> 01:03:30,450
HOW 'BOUT YOU,
WILSON?

825
01:03:30,490 --> 01:03:33,190
YOU GET INITIATED?

826
01:03:33,220 --> 01:03:37,460
YEAH, THEY HOG TIED ME TO THE
BACK STOP AND LEFT ME ALL NIGHT.

827
01:03:37,490 --> 01:03:38,590
SEE!?!

828
01:03:38,630 --> 01:03:40,090
EVERYBODY GETS
INITIATED.

829
01:03:40,130 --> 01:03:43,200
HE COULD
GET HURT.

830
01:03:43,230 --> 01:03:45,470
I AIN'T HELPIN'.

831
01:03:45,500 --> 01:03:47,170
ME NEITHER.

832
01:03:47,200 --> 01:03:50,200
AIN'T NOBODY GONNA.
HE'S OUR BEST HITTER.

833
01:03:58,350 --> 01:04:00,080
SUIT YOURSELVES.

834
01:04:04,350 --> 01:04:06,850
YOU JUST MIGHT WISH YOU
HADN'T LEFT IT UP TO ME.

835
01:04:15,300 --> 01:04:17,360
ALRIGHT, WILL,
COME HERE.

836
01:04:19,500 --> 01:04:21,370
