AND TELL ME WHATCHA THINK.

837
01:04:25,110 --> 01:04:27,210
MAYBE A BIT THICKER
THAN I'M USED TO.

838
01:04:27,240 --> 01:04:31,040
ALRIGHT...
LET ME SEE.

839
01:04:31,080 --> 01:04:32,950
I THINK I KNOW
WHAT IT NEEDS.

840
01:04:42,960 --> 01:04:44,660
MORE LEMONADE?

841
01:04:44,690 --> 01:04:46,490
YES,
THANK YOU.

842
01:04:56,710 --> 01:04:58,970
IT'S A LOT LIKE
MY MOM'S.

843
01:05:01,680 --> 01:05:04,610
GINNIE, WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOUR MOM?

844
01:05:04,650 --> 01:05:07,210
WELL, IT'S NOT
A LONG STORY.

845
01:05:07,250 --> 01:05:09,420
SHE DIED
WHEN I WAS BORN.

846
01:05:09,450 --> 01:05:12,050
BEEN DADDY 'N ME
EVER SINCE.

847
01:05:12,090 --> 01:05:14,190
I'M SORRY.

848
01:05:14,220 --> 01:05:16,460
