FOR HIM.

872
01:06:55,710 --> 01:06:57,640
THANK YA.

873
01:06:57,680 --> 01:06:59,680
GOOD TALKIN' TO YA,
GINNIE.

874
01:06:59,710 --> 01:07:01,040
GOOD NIGHT,
YA'LL.

875
01:07:01,080 --> 01:07:01,640
'NIGHT, WILL.

876
01:07:01,680 --> 01:07:03,280
GOOD NIGHT.

877
01:07:07,820 --> 01:07:12,020
[MUSIC]

878
01:07:19,800 --> 01:07:23,230
