THIS ON FOR SIZE?

880
01:07:32,580 --> 01:07:34,610
[GRUNTS AND GROANS]

881
01:07:38,150 --> 01:07:39,150
YOU IDIOT!

882
01:07:39,180 --> 01:07:41,150
