KILLED ME!

883
01:07:41,190 --> 01:07:43,120
A SHAME IT DIDN'T.

884
01:07:43,150 --> 01:07:45,520
EVERYTHING JUST GOES
YOUR WAY, DON'T IT?

885
01:07:45,560 --> 01:07:47,390
