AND HURT A LITTLE.

888
01:07:51,760 --> 01:07:53,560
I RECKON IT SERVES
YOU RIGHT.

889
01:07:55,300 --> 01:07:56,570
[SHOUTS IN PAIN]

890
01:08:00,340 --> 01:08:01,770
