SNAKE BIT BEFORE.

892
01:08:03,540 --> 01:08:04,540
IT AIN'T NOTHIN'.

893
01:08:04,580 --> 01:08:06,380
NO, YOU NEED TO GET
TO A DOCTOR!

894
01:08:06,410 --> 01:08:08,540
I DON'T NEED
ANY HELP FROM YOU!

895
01:08:19,690 --> 01:08:22,530
YOU KNOW, PIKE, PROB'BLY WENT
TO GIT HIM A JAR A' SHINE.

896
01:08:22,560 --> 01:08:24,830
