JUST QUIT TRYIN' TO SHOVE

1168
01:26:39,970 --> 01:26:42,440
RELIGION DOWN EVERYBODY
ELSE'S THROAT!

1169
01:27:06,320 --> 01:27:07,550
HEY, JOHN.

1170
01:27:07,590 --> 01:27:09,350
HEY, CHICK.

1171
01:27:09,390 --> 01:27:11,450
HEY, CAN YOU GIVE ME
A HAND A SECOND?

1172
01:27:11,490 --> 01:27:13,290
SURE, WHAT DO
YOU NEED?

1173
01:27:13,320 --> 01:27:15,660
TURN THAT THING
ABOUT A QUARTER TURN.

1174
01:27:19,860 --> 01:27:23,470
OH, YEAH, THAT'S
GOOD, THAT'S GOOD.

1175
01:27:23,500 --> 01:27:26,300
