1180
01:27:39,780 --> 01:27:42,420
THERE ARE SOME
CHRISTIANS THAT DRINK.

1181
01:27:42,450 --> 01:27:45,820
WHOLE DENOMINATIONS
ALLOW "MODERATE DRINK."

1182
01:27:45,860 --> 01:27:49,020
I DON'T SEE HOW
THEY CAN JUSTIFY IT,

1183
01:27:49,060 --> 01:27:52,430
BUT THEY SAY AS LONG
AS THEY DRINK IN PRIVATE

1184
01:27:52,460 --> 01:27:57,630
OR DRINK JUST A LITTLE BIT THEY
WON'T HEAR ANY DIFFERENT-

1185
01:27:57,670 --> 01:27:59,970
