THE LAW OF THE LAND.

1186
01:28:00,000 --> 01:28:03,370
BUT THERE'S ONE THING
I DON'T HEAR 'EM SAY.

1187
01:28:03,410 --> 01:28:05,710
(CHICK)
WHAT?

1188
01:28:05,740 --> 01:28:07,310
(JOHN) THEY DON'T SAY
THEY'RE DRINKING

1189
01:28:07,340 --> 01:28:10,310
SO THAT GOD WILL BE
GLORIFIED IN THEIR LIVES.

1190
01:28:10,350 --> 01:28:11,580
(CHICK)
RECKON NOT.

1191
01:28:11,620 --> 01:28:13,080
(JOHN)
BUT THAT IS BIBLE.

1192
01:28:13,120 --> 01:28:14,950
"WHETHER THEREFORE,
YE EAT, OR DRINK,

1193
01:28:14,990 --> 01:28:19,820
OR WHATSOEVER YOU DO,
DO ALL TO THE GLORY OF GOD."

1194
01:28:19,860 --> 01:28:22,860
PEOPLE DON'T OFTEN THINK
ABOUT GOD'S GLORY.

1195
01:28:22,890 --> 01:28:28,430
THEY THINK ABOUT THEIR
OWN PLEASURES INSTEAD.

1196
01:28:28,470 --> 01:28:32,430
(CHICK) SO YOU THINK
PROHIBITION'S TH' RIGHT THING?

1197
01:28:32,470 --> 01:28:35,100
(JOHN) WELL, THIS
MAY SURPRISE YOU,

1198
