BUT SOMETIMES I WORRY ABOUT
THE EFFECTS OF PROHIBITION.

1199
01:28:39,140 --> 01:28:40,910
I FEEL LIKE
IT'S MADE IT HARDER

1200
01:28:40,940 --> 01:28:42,980
TO REACH SOME PEOPLE
WITH THE GOSPEL.

1201
01:28:43,010 --> 01:28:44,780
REALLY?

1202
01:28:44,820 --> 01:28:46,580
IF CHRISTIANS EVER
COME TO THE PLACE

1203
01:28:46,620 --> 01:28:48,680
WHERE WE THINK WE CAN
MAKE PEOPLE ACT LIKE

1204
01:28:48,720 --> 01:28:53,090
THEY KNOW THE LORD EVEN WHEN
THEY DON'T, THEY'LL HATE US.

1205
01:28:53,120 --> 01:28:55,420
AND MAYBE RIGHTLY SO.

1206
01:28:55,460 --> 01:28:58,690
THE CHOICE TO COME TO CHRIST
IS A CHOICE MADE IN THE HEART.

1207
01:28:58,730 --> 01:29:01,100
IT CAN'T BE FORCED
ON SOMEONE.

1208
01:29:01,130 --> 01:29:04,830
NOW, I KNOW THAT LIQUOR
IS THE BANE OF OUR SOCIETY.

1209
01:29:04,870 --> 01:29:08,840
AND I KNOW THAT LIVES ARE BEING
SAVED BY THE 18TH AMENDMENT.

1210
01:29:08,870 --> 01:29:11,610
BUT THE ROOT OF THE PROBLEM
IS STILL SIN

1211
01:29:11,640 --> 01:29:14,480
