THAT, CHICK.

1220
01:29:51,480 --> 01:29:53,010
GIVE ME A HAND.

1221
01:29:59,190 --> 01:30:01,060
PICK IT UP JUST A LITTLE.

1222
01:30:01,090 --> 01:30:02,890
THERE YOU GO.

1223
01:30:02,930 --> 01:30:09,730
ALRIGHT.

1224
01:30:09,770 --> 01:30:12,430
I DON'T UNDERSTAND
WHAT I'M DOIN' WRONG.

1225
01:30:12,470 --> 01:30:14,700
I'VE ONLY BEEN A CHRISTIAN
FOR A FEW DAYS.

1226
01:30:14,740 --> 01:30:17,570
BUT, IT SEEMS NO ONE ON
THE TEAM KIN STAND ME.

1227
01:30:17,610 --> 01:30:18,710
EVEN WILL.

1228
01:30:18,740 --> 01:30:22,110
HE SAID I'M ACTIN'
LIKE A HOLY ROLLER.

1229
01:30:22,150 --> 01:30:23,440
WILL SAID THAT?

1230
01:30:23,480 --> 01:30:26,110
YES, SIR.

1231
01:30:26,150 --> 01:30:31,120
BUT THEN, I GIVE HIM
HIS FIRST DRINK.

1232
01:30:31,160 --> 01:30:33,020
I KNOW I'LL HAVE
TO ANSWER FOR THAT.

1233
01:30:33,060 --> 01:30:35,990
GINNIE TOLD ME HE TOOK
A PLEDGE NOT TO DRINK.

1234
01:30:36,030 --> 01:30:39,860
