COULD TAKE FRIDAY OFF?

1242
01:31:05,760 --> 01:31:08,160
I'M TRYING TO ORGANIZE A DAY
TRIP FOR THE MILL BOYS,

1243
01:31:08,190 --> 01:31:10,790
AND I SURE COULD
USE A HAND.

1244
01:31:10,830 --> 01:31:14,130
AH, YOU CAN
COUNT ON ME.

1245
01:31:14,160 --> 01:31:18,870
DO YOU THINK IT WOULD BE ALRIGHT
IF I BRUNG WILL ALONG, TOO?

1246
01:31:18,900 --> 01:31:21,000
