1255
01:32:01,960 --> 01:32:04,960
[EXCITED SCREAMING]

1256
01:32:21,350 --> 01:32:24,550
[EXCITED SCREAMING]

1257
01:32:37,060 --> 01:32:40,260
ALRIGHT, EVERYBODY STAY
TOGETHER AS A GROUP.

1258
01:32:40,300 --> 01:32:42,130
AND NOBODY IS TO GO OUT
IN THE WATER

1259
01:32:42,170 --> 01:32:44,170
DEEPER THAN WHAT
YOU CAN STAND IN.

1260
01:32:44,200 --> 01:32:45,000
RIGHT?

1261
01:32:45,040 --> 01:32:46,170
RIGHT.

1262
01:32:46,210 --> 01:32:47,870
AND THESE ARE YOUR
TWO LIFEGUARDS.

1263
01:32:47,910 --> 01:32:49,640
YOU DO WHATEVER
THEY TELL YOU TO DO.

1264
01:32:49,680 --> 01:32:52,010
