THE BACK OF THE TRUCK

1265
01:32:52,050 --> 01:32:53,280
WITH ME AND GINNIE,
RIGHT?

1266
01:32:53,310 --> 01:32:54,750
RIGHT.

1267
01:32:54,780 --> 01:32:57,720
AND EVERYBODY KEEP YOUR
LONG JOHNS ON ALL DAY!

1268
01:32:57,750 --> 01:32:58,180
