1271
01:33:00,020 --> 01:33:01,290
RIGHT!

1272
01:33:01,320 --> 01:33:02,850
GO IN!

1273
01:33:02,890 --> 01:33:05,690
[EXCITED SCREAMING]

1274
01:33:13,800 --> 01:33:15,000
PRISONERS HAVE BEEN
SET FREE!

1275
01:33:15,040 --> 01:33:16,800
YEAH.

1276
01:33:33,320 --> 01:33:34,920
I SEE YOU LIKE TO
SPLASH, HUH!

1277
01:33:37,060 --> 01:33:38,060
CAN I BE NEXT?

1278
01:33:38,090 --> 01:33:39,320
YEAH,
YOU CAN BE NEXT.

1279
01:33:41,830 --> 01:33:43,390
OKAY,
YOU TOO.

1280
01:33:43,430 --> 01:33:45,060
LINE UP
FOR CANNON BALLS!

1281
01:33:56,380 --> 01:33:58,210
