INTERRUPTIN'.

1282
01:33:58,240 --> 01:34:00,280
WELL, YA ARE,
BUT THAT DOESN'T MEAN

1283
01:34:00,310 --> 01:34:02,850
THAT THE INTERRUPTION
IS UNWELCOME.

1284
01:34:05,790 --> 01:34:07,690
WILL, I WANTED TO ASK
YA SOMETHIN' ANYWAY.

1285
01:34:07,720 --> 01:34:10,090
ALRIGHT, ASK AWAY.

1286
01:34:12,960 --> 01:34:15,290
ALRIGHT...

1287
01:34:15,330 --> 01:34:18,900
WELL...

1288
01:34:18,930 --> 01:34:22,930
WILL, HAVE YOU KEPT YOUR
PROMISE TO YOUR MAMA?

1289
01:34:27,910 --> 01:34:32,180
WELL, I GUESS THERE'S NO
USE TRYIN' TO FOOL YA.

1290
01:34:32,210 --> 01:34:34,280
I KEPT IT TIL THE NIGHT PIKE
INITIATED ME TO THE TEAM

1291
01:34:34,310 --> 01:34:37,150
WITH A FULL GROWN
COPPERHEAD.

1292
01:34:37,180 --> 01:34:41,750
THEN, I STARTED DRINKIN'
WITH THE TEAM.

1293
01:34:41,790 --> 01:34:44,020
I WAS TOO ASHAMED TO TELL
YOU ON THE ROAD INTO TOWN

1294
01:34:44,060 --> 01:34:46,220
AND SO I TOLD YOU ABOUT
THE PROMISE I MADE

1295
01:34:46,260 --> 01:34:49,190
AND I SET OUT
TO KEEP IT.

1296
01:34:49,230 --> 01:34:51,430
HAVE YA?

1297
01:34:51,460 --> 01:34:54,930
I DID FOR A WHILE.

1298
01:34:54,970 --> 01:34:58,100
