THAT'S DANGEROUS.

1301
01:35:02,040 --> 01:35:03,210
I KNOW.

1302
01:35:03,240 --> 01:35:06,440
MY PA HAD A BROTHER THAT DRANK
HIMSELF TO DEATH, AS THEY SAY.

1303
01:35:06,480 --> 01:35:09,010
THAT'S WHY HE NEVER
WANTED EITHER OF US BOYS

1304
01:35:09,050 --> 01:35:10,050
TO EVEN TOUCH IT.

1305
01:35:10,080 --> 01:35:11,780
THEN, WHAT POSSESSED
YOU TO DO IT?

1306
01:35:11,820 --> 01:35:14,750
UH, I JUST FIGURED I WAS OLD
ENOUGH TO MAKE MY OWN CHOICES

1307
01:35:14,790 --> 01:35:18,420
AND NOT DO WHATEVER
MY PARENTS SAID.

1308
01:35:18,460 --> 01:35:22,160
SO, YOU DIDN'T TELL
THE TRUTH THAT NIGHT.

1309
01:35:22,200 --> 01:35:26,830
NO. I'M SORRY,
GINNIE.

1310
01:35:26,870 --> 01:35:28,070
WILL, YOU NEED
TO GET HELP.

1311
01:35:28,100 --> 01:35:31,770
NO, I DON'T NEED HELP, I JUST
NEED TO QUIT IT, AND I WILL.

1312
01:35:31,810 --> 01:35:33,170
IN YOUR OWN STRENGTH?

1313
01:35:33,210 --> 01:35:37,180
WELL, I'M NOT GONNA LET
ANYONE ELSE DO IT FOR ME.

1314
01:35:37,210 --> 01:35:45,750
LOOK, GINNIE, I'VE NEVER
KNOWN ANYONE TO CARE ABOUT.

1315
01:35:45,790 --> 01:35:47,290
