1320
01:35:58,200 --> 01:36:01,200
NO. NO, I CARE ABOUT YOU TOO,
WILL WRIGHT.

1321
01:36:01,230 --> 01:36:03,330
TOO MUCH TO IGNORE
YOUR WALK WITH GOD.

1322
01:36:03,370 --> 01:36:04,900
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

1323
01:36:04,940 --> 01:36:07,770
YOU JUST ADMITTED THAT YOU
WANT TO DO IT ALL ON YOUR OWN.

1324
01:36:07,810 --> 01:36:10,440
YOU!
IT'S ALL YOU.

1325
01:36:10,480 --> 01:36:12,840
YOU'RE TOO PROUD
TO GET HELP.

1326
01:36:12,880 --> 01:36:15,910
WILL, ARE YOU
A CHRISTIAN?

1327
01:36:15,950 --> 01:36:16,950
WHAT DO YOU
WANT ME TO SAY?

1328
01:36:16,980 --> 01:36:18,820
I TOLD YOU I'VE BEEN
A CHRISTIAN MY WHOLE LIFE.

1329
01:36:18,850 --> 01:36:20,780
