WHAT YOU SAY.

1330
01:36:20,820 --> 01:36:21,950
BUT I DON'T SEE-

1331
01:36:21,990 --> 01:36:24,320
WHAT?
WHAT DON'T YOU SEE?

1332
01:36:24,360 --> 01:36:27,060
WILL, ARE YOU A CHRISTIAN
IN YOUR HEART?

1333
01:36:27,090 --> 01:36:29,190
OR ARE THEY
JUST WORDS YOU SAY?

1334
01:36:33,870 --> 01:36:38,040
YOU KNOW WHAT?
YOU'RE RIGHT.

1335
01:36:38,070 --> 01:36:42,040
GINNIE, I'VE BEEN
WRONG AND I'M SORRY.

1336
01:36:42,080 --> 01:36:44,080
WILL YOU FORGIVE ME
AND GIVE ME ANOTHER CHANCE?

1337
01:36:44,110 --> 01:36:45,080
FORGIVE YOU FOR WHAT?

1338
01:36:45,110 --> 01:36:46,580
FOR DRINKIN'.

1339
01:36:46,610 --> 01:36:49,350
I NEVER SHOULD
HAVE LIED TO YOU.

1340
01:36:49,380 --> 01:36:51,180
GINNIE, I KNOW IN
MY HEART I CAN QUIT.

1341
01:36:51,220 --> 01:36:52,380
I'LL EVEN GET HELP.

1342
01:36:52,420 --> 01:36:54,320
ARE YOU JUST SAYIN'
THAT TO PLEASE ME?

1343
01:36:54,350 --> 01:36:55,920
GINNIE, I'LL DO
WHATEVER YOU WANT.

1344
01:36:55,960 --> 01:36:59,220
NO! NO YOU CAN'T
JUST DO WHAT I WANT.

1345
01:36:59,260 --> 01:37:03,190
WILL, IN YOUR HEART DO YOU
WANT TO PLEASE JESUS CHRIST

1346
01:37:03,230 --> 01:37:07,300
BECAUSE YOU BELONG TO HIM,
BODY AND SOUL?

1347
01:37:07,330 --> 01:37:09,200
OR DO YOU JUST
WANT TO PLEASE ME?

1348
01:37:09,240 --> 01:37:11,600
CAN'T I DO BOTH?

1349
01:37:11,640 --> 01:37:19,310
THIS FRIENDSHIP BETWEEN US -
WHATEVER IT IS - IT HAS TO END.

1350
01:37:19,350 --> 01:37:21,350
I'M SORRY, WILL.

1351
01:37:21,380 --> 01:37:25,050
BUT I AM NOT
HELPIN' YOU.

1352
01:37:25,080 --> 01:37:27,620
GINNIE.

1353
01:37:27,650 --> 01:37:31,290
I'M SORRY,
I CAN'T...

