DON'T PUSH ME.

1389
01:42:17,610 --> 01:42:18,810
YEAH?

1390
01:42:18,840 --> 01:42:23,450
I SEEN THE GAME, YOU COULDN'T
HIT ME EVEN IF'N YA WAS TO TRY.

1391
01:42:27,550 --> 01:42:28,720
THERE HE IS,
CHICK!

1392
01:42:28,750 --> 01:42:30,590
PIKE,
LEAVE HIM ALONE!

1393
01:42:30,620 --> 01:42:32,790
YA HERE THAT,
IRON WILL?

1394
01:42:32,830 --> 01:42:35,530
