ME AND THE TOWN BOY.

1400
01:42:46,810 --> 01:42:49,240
I AIN'T FIGHTING
A ONE-ARMED MAN!

1401
01:42:49,280 --> 01:42:51,410
DON'T YOU WALK
AWAY FROM ME!

1402
01:42:54,580 --> 01:42:55,450
[WACK!]

1403
01:42:58,580 --> 01:42:59,380
I SAID-
LEEEEAVE ME ALOOOOONE!!!!

1404
01:42:59,420 --> 01:43:00,420
[WACK!]

1405
01:43:06,560 --> 01:43:09,390
C'MON BO? BO.

1406
01:43:09,430 --> 01:43:11,800
NO. NO!!

1407
01:43:11,830 --> 01:43:13,700
WILL, WHAT DID
YOU DO?

1408
01:43:13,730 --> 01:43:15,530
YOU KILLED HIM.

1409
01:43:15,570 --> 01:43:16,470
YOU KILLED HIM!!!

1410
01:43:16,500 --> 01:43:21,240
NO. PLEASE, GOD, NO!

1411
01:43:32,550 --> 01:43:34,920
HE AIN'T DEAD!

1412
01:43:34,950 --> 01:43:36,450
HE'S STILL
BREATHING!

1413
01:43:36,490 --> 01:43:38,790
PIKE, WE GOTTA GET HIM
TO THE INFIRMARY!

1414
01:43:38,820 --> 01:43:40,760
RUN AHEAD
AND GET THE DOC.

1415
01:43:42,560 --> 01:43:43,460
PIKE!

1416
01:43:55,310 --> 01:43:59,410
IT'S A BAD BUMP, BUT HE'S
BREATHING STEADILY NOW.

1417
01:43:59,450 --> 01:44:01,480
AND HE'S GOING
TO BE OKAY.

1418
01:44:14,430 --> 01:44:17,660
WILL,
BO'S NOT DEAD.

1419
01:44:17,700 --> 01:44:19,660
HE'S KNOCKED OUT
BUT HE AIN'T DEAD.

1420
01:44:19,700 --> 01:44:21,300
DON'T DO
ANYTHING CRAZY!

1421
01:44:21,330 --> 01:44:22,600
JUST LEAVE
ME ALONE.

1422
01:44:22,630 --> 01:44:26,740
NO, I'M NOT GOIN'
ANYWHERE.

1423
01:44:26,770 --> 01:44:27,540
THEN I'LL GO-

1424
01:44:27,570 --> 01:44:29,670
NO, YOU'RE STAYIN'
'TIL WE TALK.

1425
01:44:29,710 --> 01:44:33,310
THERE'S NOTHING
TO TALK ABOUT.

1426
01:44:33,350 --> 01:44:35,810
ALL I COULD THINK ABOUT WAS HOW
MUCH I HATED YOUR BROTHER.

1427
01:44:35,850 --> 01:44:38,950
HOW I WANTED
TO HURT HIM BAD.

1428
01:44:38,990 --> 01:44:40,550
BUT IF BO DIES-

1429
01:44:40,590 --> 01:44:41,690
BO AIN'T GONNA DIE.

1430
01:44:41,720 --> 01:44:42,820
YOU DON'T KNOW THAT!

1431
01:44:42,860 --> 01:44:46,290
I KNOW HE'S
IN GOD'S HANDS.

1432
01:44:46,330 --> 01:44:47,660
WE KIN PRAY FOR HIM.

1433
01:44:47,690 --> 01:44:52,330
DON'T - TALK TO ME -
ABOUT GOD!

1434
01:44:52,370 --> 01:44:54,600
YOU WON'T EVEN
PRAY FOR HIM?

1435
01:44:54,630 --> 01:44:56,470
GOD WON'T HEAR
MY PRAYER.

1436
01:44:56,500 --> 01:44:57,940
SURE HE WILL.

1437
01:44:57,970 --> 01:44:59,300
GOD HEARS
ALL PRAYERS.

1438
01:44:59,340 --> 01:45:01,670
YOU DON'T KNOW YOUR
BIBLE LIKE I DO.

1439
01:45:01,710 --> 01:45:04,470
THE BIBLE SAYS IF THERE'S SIN
IN MY HEART, GOD WON'T HEAR ME.

1440
01:45:04,510 --> 01:45:07,710
THEN GET RID
OF THE SIN.

1441
01:45:07,750 --> 01:45:10,680
THET'S ALL THE BIBLE
I DO KNOW.

1442
01:45:10,720 --> 01:45:15,420
MR. SUNDAY SAID, IF YA TURN FROM
YER SIN, GOD'LL FORGIVE YA.

1443
01:45:15,450 --> 01:45:17,350
HE WANTS TO.

1444
01:45:17,390 --> 01:45:19,420
THAT'S ALL THERE IS
TO BEIN' A CHRISTIAN

1445
01:45:19,460 --> 01:45:22,630
JUST ASKIN' JESUS FORGIVENESS
FOR YER SINS.

1446
01:45:22,660 --> 01:45:24,690
IT'S NOT
THAT SIMPLE.

1447
01:45:24,730 --> 01:45:27,600
WHY NOT?

1448
01:45:27,630 --> 01:45:30,400
MY WHOLE LIFE
IS A LIE.

1449
01:45:30,440 --> 01:45:33,070
I'VE ALWAYS SAID WHATEVER
PEOPLE WANTED TO HEAR.

1450
01:45:33,110 --> 01:45:36,340
BUT IN MY HEART I NEVER
TURNED FROM MY SIN.

1451
01:45:36,380 --> 01:45:38,110
YA KIN CHANGE THET.

1452
01:45:38,140 --> 01:45:41,810
I'VE HEARD ABOUT BEING
A CHRISTIAN FOR SO LONG-

1453
01:45:41,850 --> 01:45:43,550
IT'S NOTHIN'
BUT WORDS.

1454
01:45:43,580 --> 01:45:45,720
DON'T JIST
SAY THE WORDS.

1455
01:45:45,750 --> 01:45:46,820
MEAN 'EM.

1456
01:45:46,850 --> 01:45:49,820
IT AIN'T THET
HARD TO DO.

1457
01:45:49,860 --> 01:45:52,460
I WOULDN'T EVEN
KNOW HOW...

1458
01:45:52,490 --> 01:45:55,430
WILL, ARE YA SORRY
FOR YER SINS?

1459
01:45:55,460 --> 01:45:56,690
I AM.

1460
01:45:56,730 --> 01:45:58,430
DON'T TELL ME.

1461
01:45:58,460 --> 01:46:00,330
TELL HIM.

1462
01:46:03,000 --> 01:46:08,370
I AM SORRY
FOR MY SIN.

1463
01:46:08,410 --> 01:46:12,080
GOD, I'M SORRY FOR GOING AGAINST
YOU AND GOING MY OWN WAY -

1464
01:46:12,110 --> 01:46:13,940
FOR SAYIN' THAT
I WAS A CHRISTIAN

1465
01:46:13,980 --> 01:46:18,980
AND DOIN' WHATEVER
I WANTED TO DO.

1466
01:46:19,020 --> 01:46:23,120
I'M SORRY - FOR EVERYTHING
THAT I'VE DONE AGAINST YOU.

1467
01:46:23,160 --> 01:46:27,460
GOD, FORGIVE ME
FOR MY SIN.

1468
01:46:27,490 --> 01:46:29,060
PLEASE FORGIVE ME.

1469
01:46:35,530 --> 01:46:36,830
WERE YA JUST PRETENDIN'?

1470
01:46:36,870 --> 01:46:39,970
NO.

1471
01:46:40,010 --> 01:46:43,970
LET'S PRAY
FOR BO. OKAY?

1472
01:46:44,010 --> 01:46:45,810
YEAH.
OKAY.

1473
01:46:52,720 --> 01:46:53,720
[KNOCK, KNOCK, KNOCK]

1474
01:46:53,750 --> 01:46:55,590
YEAH.

1475
01:46:55,620 --> 01:46:56,850
CAN I TALK TO YOU
FOR A MINUTE?

1476
01:46:56,890 --> 01:46:58,590
SURE, COME ON IN.

1477
01:47:04,600 --> 01:47:06,630
I HEARD ABOUT
WHAT HAPPENED.

1478
01:47:06,670 --> 01:47:08,500
BUT, YOU DIDN'T HEAR
ALL OF IT.

1479
01:47:08,530 --> 01:47:10,470
I ASKED THE LORD
TO SAVE ME.

1480
01:47:10,500 --> 01:47:11,970
IS THAT RIGHT?

1481
01:47:12,000 --> 01:47:13,870
I'VE NEVER BEEN ABLE TO LOOK
SOMEONE IN THE EYE BEFORE

1482
01:47:13,910 --> 01:47:16,570
AND TELL THEM THAT
I KNOW I'M A CHRISTIAN.

1483
01:47:16,610 --> 01:47:19,180
BUT I CAN TODAY.

1484
01:47:19,210 --> 01:47:21,610
THAT'S AN ANSWER
TO PRAYER, WILL.

1485
01:47:25,050 --> 01:47:27,420
BUT THERE'S STILL SO
MUCH I DON'T KNOW.

1486
01:47:30,620 --> 01:47:32,720
WHEN I LEFT HOME -
THAT WAS WRONG.

1487
01:47:32,760 --> 01:47:34,020
WHEN I BROKE MY PROMISE
AND STARTED TO DRINK -

1488
01:47:34,060 --> 01:47:36,760
THAT WAS WRONG.

1489
01:47:36,800 --> 01:47:39,500
LETTING MY TEAM DOWN BECAUSE
OF MY DRINKIN'...IS MORE WRONG.

1490
01:47:39,530 --> 01:47:42,470
LYING AND ACTIN' LIKE
I'M SOMETHING I WASN'T.

1491
01:47:43,940 --> 01:47:45,970
I'M SO WRONG;
I DON'T KNOW HOW TO GET RIGHT!

1492
01:47:46,000 --> 01:47:49,010
I DON'T EVEN KNOW IF I SHOULD
PLAY BASEBALL ANYMORE.

1493
01:47:49,040 --> 01:47:51,980
IT'S BEEN MY
WHOLE LIFE -

1494
01:47:52,010 --> 01:47:55,010
I - I JUST
DON'T KNOW!

1495
01:47:59,820 --> 01:48:03,650
IS BASEBALL
REALLY THE PROBLEM?

1496
01:48:03,690 --> 01:48:05,260
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

1497
01:48:05,290 --> 01:48:08,930
WELL, WHAT DID
BILLY SUNDAY SAY?

1498
01:48:08,960 --> 01:48:11,800
HE SAID HE DIDN'T HAVE
A PROBLEM WITH THE GAME ITSELF.

1499
01:48:11,830 --> 01:48:15,730
HE SAID HE FOUND
A HIGHER CALLING.

1500
01:48:15,770 --> 01:48:18,770
YOU'VE GOT A NATURAL
GIFT FOR BASEBALL.

1501
01:48:18,800 --> 01:48:21,570
I'VE WATCHED YOU DEVELOP IT
ALL SEASON.

1502
01:48:21,610 --> 01:48:24,610
YOU'VE GOT A GIFT FOR
WORKING WITH THE BOYS.

1503
01:48:24,640 --> 01:48:26,840
I'VE SEEN THAT
THIS SUMMER, TOO.

1504
01:48:26,880 --> 01:48:30,280
MAYBE YOU CAN FIND A WAY TO
TAKE ALL THAT GOD'S GIVEN YOU

1505
01:48:30,320 --> 01:48:33,850
AND BRING GLORY TO HIM.

1506
01:48:33,890 --> 01:48:36,250
I'M WILLING TO DO
WHATEVER IT TAKES.

1507
01:48:36,290 --> 01:48:38,990
THEN HE'LL MAKE IT
CLEAR TO YOU.

1508
01:48:39,020 --> 01:48:42,130
"IN ALL THY WAYS
ACKNOWLEDGE HIM."

1509
01:48:42,160 --> 01:48:44,600
HE'LL DIRECT YOU.

1510
01:48:44,630 --> 01:48:47,730
FIRST OFF, I HAVE A LOT OF
APOLOGIES I NEED TO MAKE.

1511
01:48:47,770 --> 01:48:50,730
SOUNDS LIKE A GOOD START.

1512
01:48:50,770 --> 01:48:52,070
CAN I SPEAK TO GINNIE?

1513
01:48:52,100 --> 01:48:54,700
WILL! BO'S AWAKE!
HE'S FINE!!

1514
01:48:57,040 --> 01:48:58,840
HE JUST WOKE UP.
HE'S GONNA BE ALRIGHT.

1515
01:48:58,880 --> 01:49:00,010
CAN I GO SEE HIM?

1516
01:49:00,050 --> 01:49:01,750
THET'S WHY I COME
TO GET YA!

1517
01:49:04,020 --> 01:49:04,980
CAN I COME
BACK LATER?

1518
01:49:05,020 --> 01:49:06,950
SURE, GO ON.

1519
01:49:18,330 --> 01:49:22,870
MRS. SPANGLER, I'M SO SORRY
ABOUT WHAT I DID.

1520
01:49:22,900 --> 01:49:26,000
HAS BO -
IS HE AWAKE YET?

1521
01:49:26,040 --> 01:49:28,140
