BUT HE'LL BE FINE.

1523
01:49:30,110 --> 01:49:31,340
HE'S UP.

1524
01:49:31,380 --> 01:49:33,280
I'M SO GLAD
TO HEAR THAT.

1525
01:49:33,310 --> 01:49:34,410
