I GO AND SEE HIM?

1526
01:49:34,450 --> 01:49:37,710
AS A MATTER OF FACT, HE
ASKED ABOUT YOU FIRST THING.

1527
01:49:37,750 --> 01:49:38,580
REALLY?

1528
01:49:38,620 --> 01:49:39,820
YES.

1529
01:49:39,850 --> 01:49:42,720
HE WANTS TO MAKE SURE YOU DON'T
FEEL BAD ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED!

1530
01:49:42,750 --> 01:49:44,120
HE DOES?

1531
01:49:44,160 --> 01:49:45,990
THERE IS NOTHIN'
YOU CAN DO

1532
01:49:46,020 --> 01:49:50,030
TO DIM THAT BOY'S ADMIRATION
OF YOU, WILL WRIGHT.

1533
01:49:52,160 --> 01:49:54,260
HE'S WAITIN' IN
THERE FOR YA.

1534
01:49:54,300 --> 01:49:56,030
GO ON IN.

1535
01:50:06,650 --> 01:50:08,010
IT'S AMAZING.

1536
01:50:08,050 --> 01:50:10,610
FOR THE FIRST TIME IN MY LIFE,
I FEEL FREE!

1537
01:50:10,650 --> 01:50:14,750
IT DOES KINDA SEEM LIKE YOU'RE
BOUNCING OFF THE CLOUDS.

1538
01:50:14,790 --> 01:50:18,150
TO THINK FOR SO LONG I LIVED
TRYIN' TO ACT LIKE I WAS FREE -

1539
01:50:18,190 --> 01:50:20,160
I NEVER KNEW
HOW IT FEELS!

1540
01:50:20,190 --> 01:50:21,860
AND NOW I BET YOU'RE
JUST ITCHIN' TO GET BACK

1541
01:50:21,890 --> 01:50:23,660
INTO THE BATTER'S BOX.

1542
01:50:23,700 --> 01:50:25,300
WELL, THAT
I DON'T KNOW.

1543
01:50:25,330 --> 01:50:27,030
I APOLOGIZED TO THE TEAM
AT PRACTICE,

1544
01:50:27,070 --> 01:50:29,130
BUT SCOOP SAYS
HE STILL WON'T PLAY ME.

1545
01:50:29,170 --> 01:50:30,630
