NOT SEE YA PLAY?

1547
01:50:32,240 --> 01:50:33,270
HE MIGHT NOT.

1548
01:50:33,310 --> 01:50:34,440
BUT WHO KNOWS?

1549
01:50:34,470 --> 01:50:36,810
MAYBE SCOOP'LL CHANGE HIS TUNE
IF I SHOW UP AND ACT RIGHT.

1550
01:50:36,840 --> 01:50:38,070
I HOPE SO.

1551
01:50:38,110 --> 01:50:40,780
IT USED TO MEAN THE WORLD TO ME
IF I CAUGHT THE EYE OF A SCOUT.

1552
01:50:40,810 --> 01:50:42,280
I KNOW.

1553
01:50:42,310 --> 01:50:43,410
DON'T GET ME WRONG.

1554
01:50:43,450 --> 01:50:46,020
IT'S STILL THE CHANCE
OF A LIFETIME.

1555
01:50:46,050 --> 01:50:47,180
BUT THERE ARE SO MANY
OTHER THINGS I CARE ABOUT

1556
01:50:47,220 --> 01:50:48,820
MORE THAN BASEBALL.

1557
01:50:48,850 --> 01:50:50,320
LIKE...

1558
01:50:50,360 --> 01:50:53,820
WELL, BO -
HIM BEING OKAY.

1559
01:50:53,860 --> 01:50:56,060
I'M GOING TO GO SEE HIM AT THE
HOSPITAL RIGHT BEFORE THE GAME.

1560
01:50:56,090 --> 01:50:57,430
THAT'S A
GREAT IDEA.

1561
01:50:57,460 --> 01:50:58,900
AND OF COURSE,

1562
01:50:58,930 --> 01:51:01,670
I WANT TO BE RIGHT WHERE
GOD WANTS ME TO BE -

1563
01:51:01,700 --> 01:51:03,730
THAT MEANS THE
WORLD TO ME.

1564
01:51:03,770 --> 01:51:04,930
THAT'S THE BEST THING.

1565
01:51:04,970 --> 01:51:06,140
YEAH.

1566
01:51:06,170 --> 01:51:09,270
AND, WELL...

1567
01:51:09,310 --> 01:51:11,810
WHAT?

1568
01:51:11,840 --> 01:51:14,010
FRIENDS - THAT I'VE MADE
WHILE I'VE BEEN HERE.

1569
01:51:14,050 --> 01:51:16,210
GINNIE, I KNOW I TOLD YOU
AT THE LAKE THE OTHER DAY,

1570
01:51:16,250 --> 01:51:19,880
BUT I GOT
TO SAY IT AGAIN...

1571
01:51:19,920 --> 01:51:23,250
YOU'VE BECOME
MY BEST FRIEND.

1572
01:51:29,230 --> 01:51:30,930
I FEEL THE
SAME WAY.

