PEANUTS!

1576
01:52:16,210 --> 01:52:17,340
PEANUTS!

1577
01:52:19,350 --> 01:52:21,480
PEANUTS!
POPCORN!

1578
01:52:29,190 --> 01:52:31,760
IRON WILL!
YOU GOTTA GIT GOIN'.

1579
01:52:31,790 --> 01:52:34,090
YOUR GONNA MISS
THE FIRST INNIN'.

1580
01:52:34,130 --> 01:52:35,890
OKAY,
I'LL GET GOIN'.

1581
01:52:35,930 --> 01:52:36,830
BUT YOU KNOW I'D
DO ANYTHING

1582
01:52:36,860 --> 01:52:39,030
TO MAKE SURE YOU WERE
THERE, TOO, RIGHT?

1583
01:52:39,060 --> 01:52:41,430
IT'S OKAY.
I'M GETTIN' BETTER.

1584
01:52:41,470 --> 01:52:43,770
GOOSE EGG
GOIN' DOWN?

1585
01:52:43,800 --> 01:52:44,830
SOME.

1586
01:52:44,870 --> 01:52:47,340
CAN YOU HIT A HOME RUN
FOR ME TODAY?

1587
01:52:47,370 --> 01:52:50,070
I DON'T KNOW IF I'LL EVEN
GET A CHANCE TO BAT, BO.

1588
01:52:50,110 --> 01:52:53,180
WHY NOT?

1589
01:52:53,210 --> 01:53:00,320
WELL, GOTTA SAY IT.

1590
01:53:00,350 --> 01:53:04,920
I WAS LIVING FOR
MYSELF, BO,

1591
01:53:04,960 --> 01:53:06,920
AND I MESSED UP PRETTY
BAD FOR THE TEAM.

1592
01:53:06,960 --> 01:53:08,290
BUT THEY'LL GIVE
YOU ANOTHER CHANCE.

1593
01:53:08,330 --> 01:53:10,090
THEY JUST GOTTA!

1594
01:53:10,130 --> 01:53:12,900
WE'LL SEE.

1595
01:53:12,930 --> 01:53:15,430
BUT, HEY, I PROMISED TO GIVE YOU
A PLAY-BY-PLAY OF HOW IT WENT

1596
01:53:15,470 --> 01:53:16,900
WHEN I GET BACK, OKAY?

1597
01:53:16,940 --> 01:53:18,970
OKAY.

1598
01:53:19,000 --> 01:53:21,040
THANKS FOR COMIN'
TO SEE ME!

1599
01:53:21,070 --> 01:53:22,940
THANKS FOR BEING
MY BIGGEST FAN.

1600
01:53:54,470 --> 01:53:58,580
WILL, HIT ONE...
OUT...FOR ME.

1601
01:53:58,610 --> 01:54:00,910
