1606
01:54:48,530 --> 01:54:51,060
ANYBODY SEEN
WRIGHT TODAY?

1607
01:54:51,100 --> 01:54:52,660
I SAW HIM
THIS MORNING.

1608
01:54:52,700 --> 01:54:55,200
PROBABLY SLEEPIN' OFF HIS
MOST RECENT SPIFFLICATION.

1609
01:54:55,230 --> 01:54:58,130
NO! HE AIN'T
BEEN DRINKIN'.

1610
01:54:58,170 --> 01:55:00,470
